    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2356812340511043596.png",
                "id": "talent76532",
                "key": "雷晶投射",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷晶投射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，然後分別<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備技能</span>：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">猜拳三連擊·剪刀</span>和<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">猜拳三連擊·布</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猜拳三連擊·剪刀</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>，然後<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備技能</span>：<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猜拳三連擊·布</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">猜拳三連擊·布</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/0e809f0cd877c453ef4eb86e7d1b8cbf_1989519212788871373.png",
                "id": "talent92257",
                "key": "猜拳三連擊",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 5,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "猜拳三連擊"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷鎖鎮域</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/4baa599d0dc30449e310756e218280e2_5855391552483871150.png",
                "id": "talent97573",
                "key": "靂霆鎮鎖",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "靂霆鎮鎖"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷晶核心</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷晶核心</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色被擊倒時：</span>移除此效果，使角色<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">免於被擊倒</span>，並治療該角色到1點生命值。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/e810a8c5cbf997dc227fbf2bafa2512b_3917936167079866676.png",
                "id": "talent59088",
                "key": "雷晶核心",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷晶核心"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">雷元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">此召喚物在場時：</span>敵方執行「切換角色」行動的元素骰費用+1。（每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7228880490708627499.png",
                "id": "talent1943",
                "key": "雷鎖鎮域",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/6f0d7b0b3f0cda9d42d38485a7202bcc_1050393483892703259.png",
                "title": "雷鎖鎮域"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著雷元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點穿透傷害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素傷害+1的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[激化領域]</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_3010145147035405622.png",
                "id": "talent13717",
                "key": "雷元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備技能</span></strong></p><p>有些技能無法被直接使用，而是需要一定次數的行動輪來進行<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>。</p><p>輪到一位牌手行動時，如果該牌手的「出戰角色」正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>技能，則跳過該牌手的行動；如果技能已經完成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>，角色將會在此時直接使用此技能。（此類需要<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>的技能，無法觸發「使用技能後」效果。）</p><p>只有「出戰角色」才能<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>技能的「出戰角色」被切換到後台，技能的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">準備</span>就會被打斷。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免於被擊倒</span></strong></p><p>一些效果會使角色在生命值被降為0的時候<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免於被擊倒</span>，並治療該角色到一定生命值。</p><p>此時，角色不視為被<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">擊倒</span>過。（因此，角色所附屬的裝備和狀態不會被棄置，充能也不會被清空。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3173480065871887585.png",
                "id": "talent12983",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
